|AX| = r(1 + \cos \alpha)
|XB| = r(1 - \cos \alpha)
|CX| = |DX| = r \sin \alpha
|AX|^2 + |XB|^2 + |CX|^2 + |DX|^2  = r^2 \left( (1+\cos\alpha)^2 +(1-\cos\alpha)^2 + 2\sin^2 \alpha\right)  = r^2 \left( 2 + 2\cos^2 \alpha + 2\sin^2 \alpha \right)  = 4r^2
